{"tid":2296303,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"69歲大劉劉鑾雄親自細說六十年傳奇歲月--- 劉鑾雄講大劉","createTime":"2020-11-22T11:07:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-24T19:31:33.000Z","uid":188176,"like":2,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"03854e17789f8a68c49e2436278a1604f7027dd0","tid":2296303,"uid":188176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T11:07:05.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">我個仔仔講得岩<br />\n我可以飲十億紅酒,不過你地班賤民去旅行就係大貪唔努力</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RfW__0-ZOVk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DRfW__0-ZOVk&d=icC9UeWzMg70WCHWfTItTxURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=9806f41f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RfW__0-ZOVk</a><br />\n<br />\n千億富豪劉鑾雄，首度公開發跡秘史，曾經飽受屈辱的大劉，如何一吐烏氣矢志要起革命大翻身？「當時邊個擋我就殺邊個！」大劉獨家披露成長歲月，談家庭、談媽媽、談潔癖、談換腎、談福臨門、談股壇狙擊手、談分身家！<br />\n<br />\n被問甘比是否最後女人？大劉霸氣回應：「如果你要我答，今日一定係！」大劉於專訪中更自嘲「廢柴中嘅廢柴，懵炳中嘅懵炳」，究竟他有過甚麼遭遇？自己事自己講，劉鑾雄親自講大劉！"},{"pid":"d21ead24198cb70c70641f43de3fd8315b90c300","tid":2296303,"uid":188176,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T11:10:10.000Z","msg":"我可以著27萬條褲,150萬套西裝<br />\n你地班賤人想去旅行?死懶蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41f8d323b3d111f983874f83bfd6e881c3821444","tid":2296303,"uid":203889,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"d21ead24198cb70c70641f43de3fd8315b90c300","tid":2296303,"uid":188176,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T11:10:10.000Z","msg":"我可以著27萬條褲,150萬套西裝<br />\n你地班賤人想去旅行?死懶蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T11:12:35.000Z","msg":"咁佢有料嘅<br />\n但鄧佢當初個大婆唔抵<br />\n<br />\n對啲女星八婆就咁疏爽<br />\n送呢樣送果樣<br />\n<br />\n又唔見佢送俾同佢挨過果個？"},{"pid":"36d60c3d981c860e2c4d51df1e2f7f2adec02f2b","tid":2296303,"uid":202698,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T11:13:10.000Z","msg":"大